A fixed-price [exchange](currency) where bitcoins can be bought by those in Korea.  

Language: Korean only.

A Korean-language introduction to Bitcoin can be found at [www.buybitcoin.co.kr](http://www.buybitcoin.co.kr) and a Korean translation of [[MultiBit]] is available (1.1).

##Buy

* Buy bitcoins with South Korean won.  The exchange rate offered is relative to the latest rate from the largest BTC/USD market.

##History

The launched was announced on September 27, 2012 (3.1).

This service is operated by Bitcoin Korea corporation (3.2).

